<main>
        <div class="p-3">
            <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
            Welcome to Shoe Inventory!<br> 
            The number 1 place where you can sell, trade and buy shoes. The unique thing that sets us apart from our competitors is that we don't charge a commission fee when you sell your shoes. To get started <a href="/login" class="link-danger">Sign up</a> then click on Inventory to begin to sell your shoes. Happy selling!
            </div>
            </div>

            <h2 class="text-center text-light">Featured Shoes</h2>
            <div class="container animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">
            <ol class="container ">
            {{#each shoes as |shoe|}}
            {{>inventory-cards shoe}}
            {{/each}}
            </ol>    
            </div> 
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>